---
title: One-Pan Pork Carnitas Tacos with Lettuce, Onion, and a Lime Crema
description: Think of this as a quicker, weeknight-friendly version of carnitas, one that doesn’t involve hours of slow-cooking like the dish typically would. To create that deep, warm profile in minimal time, you’ll add a spice blend and a bit of stock to ground pork, which makes it nice, rich, and saucy. It’s the centerpiece of these tacos, which come with lots of tasty toppings that everyone can add as they please.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/one-pan-pork-carnita-tacos-337e7f15.jpg
pdf: https://www.hellofresh.com/recipecards/card/one-pan-pork-carnita-tacos-5a2b08b9a2882a5fa04ae892-a6d6a020.pdf
course: main course
source: https://www.hellofresh.com/recipes/one-pan-pork-carnita-tacos-5a2b08b9a2882a5fa04ae892
cuisine: North America
servings: 2
time required: 25 minutes
author: HelloFresh
nutrition:
  calories: 720 kcal
  fat: 40 g
  saturated fat: 14 g
  carbohydrates: 58 g
  sugar: 6 g
